G redshifts over a significantly wider area, as well\nas detailed comparisons with cosmological simulations of massive cluster\nformation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 May 2016 20:00:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Jun 2016 16:18:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-15"}
